{quote}
[PHing|http://phing.info] Is Not GNU make; it's a PHP project build system or build tool based on Apache Ant. You can do anything with it that you could do with a traditional build system like GNU make, and its use of simple XML build files and extensible PHP "task" classes make it an easy-to-use and highly flexible build framework.
{quote}

First mentioned by a customer on the [forums|http://forums.atlassian.com/thread.jspa?threadID=40134].
